" (Un)Indent in Normal mode with Shift/Tab
nnoremap <Tab> >>
nnoremap <S-Tab> <<

" (Un)Indent in Visual mode with Shift/Tab
vnoremap <Tab> >gv
vnoremap <S-Tab> <gv

" Enable "very magic" search mode
" All chracters except 0-9, a-z, A-Z, and _ have special meaning
" Allow for searching with regex
" Type ":help \v" for more information
nnoremap / /\v
vnoremap / /\v
